<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Financial X</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body, html {
            height: 100%;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.2;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #1a5f7a;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100%;
            padding: 0 5%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .content {
            max-width: 50%;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 4em;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .back-button {
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            left: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            color: #1a5f7a;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s, color 0.3s;
        }

        .back-button:hover {
            background-color: #1a5f7a;
            color: #fff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <a href="/main" class="back-button">Back</a>
    <div class="container">
        
        <div class="content">
            <h1>About Financial X</h1>
            <p>
                Your trusted partner in finance. We deliver cutting-edge solutions to maximize returns and minimize risks.
            </p>
            <p>
                Empowering you with knowledge and tools for informed financial decisions. From wealth growth to retirement planning, we're here to guide you.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>